definitions.definition: Any of various marine fish of the family Triglidae that have a large armored head and fingerlike pectoral fins used for crawling along the sea bottom.
Other fish with appearance like that of members of family Triglidae , such as certain of those in families Dactylopteridae , Peristediidae , and Scorpaenidae .
